Class List<E>

java.lang.Object
com.example.javafx_clinicmanager.List<E>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<E>
public class List<E> extends Object implements Iterable<E>
The List List class that implements a simple array-based list for Appointment and Provider. This class allows adding, removing, and retrieving elements, along with iterator support.
Author:
Deep Patel,Manan Patel
